nodes.text: Battle of unidentified planet  (Unduli and Offee)
A battle on a planet was fought between the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems during the Clone Wars.
Republic forces were led by Jedi General Luminara Unduli and her Padawan, Commander Barriss Offee, against the Separatist Droid Army on the world.
This battle can be seen towards the beginning of the Chapter 1 of Star Wars: Clone Wars. At this point, however, the battle and the planet on which it was fought, are, as yet, unidentified.
